description:
Acrylick, whose foundation and core message is rooted in music, has partnered up with the DJ lifestyle company co founded by world renowned DJ Qbert, Thud Rumble (http://www.thudrumble.com) to release a series of limited-edition co branded pieces. The Acrylick x Thud Rumble capsule collection consist of three original designs conceived and produced by Acrylick with creative input from Thud Rumble and co founder of the company, Dj Qbert. The designs are comprised of Acrylick’s and Thud Rumbles artistic take on the art of Scratching and Turntablism.

Thud Rumble
Founded in 1996 by DJ Qbert and  Ritche "Yogafrog" Desuasido, Thud Rumble was built from a shared determination to push the envelope of skratching as a science, an art and an international culture. By creating their own wholesale distribution facility and global ecommerce network, Thud Rumble has pioneered and grown to become the world’s finest and most creative artists' labels.

name: Support Philippines (T-Shirt)
description:
We want to do our part in helping with the current crisis in the Philippines caused by Super Typhoon Haiyan. We are using the same format a a past fundraising effort, since it was highly successful with raising money for the Tsunami that occurred in Japan years back. Hopefully this will offer the Philippines the same help.

As with any natural disaster, rebuilding is quite a feat. We offer a way for our supporters to also be apart of this effort, and display the inner benevolence we each possess.

The proceeds from this shirt will go toward disaster relief in Philippines. Everything about this shirt is straightforward. The design was kept basic intentionally, mainly to cut costs of production. A simple design leads to lower production costs, resulting in more money being allocated toward a charity that will aid in helping the Philippines. Our goal is to simply aid, by raising as much money as we can from this shirt. The shirts are priced at $15, We will donate approximately $10.00 to a charity. 

Shirts will ship within two weeks time.

Pre order your Support Philippines T-Shirt.

name: Men's - Raised By (T-Shirt)
description: Hip-hop has inspired and changed many lives since it’s creation. It is not only a music genre; it is a culture and lifestyle. We were lucky being able to grow up during an era where hip-hop culture surrounded us.  It was the music we listened to, style of clothing we wore, language we spoke, and way we lived. This positive surrounding and stimulation hip-hop emitted played a part in molding us into who we are today. We pay homage to what hip-hop has given us and created this graphic. We are proud to show that this culture has raised us.

name: Men's - Nostalgia (T-Shirt)
description: Nostalgia is more than just longing for the past; it is factor in our daily lives. Our beliefs in the present are built on the solid foundation of our past. Our surroundings and preferences in the past, helped guide and form who we are now as individuals. We decided to take one memory, which we believe many others can relate to, and created this design. There was a simpler time where music was analog rather than digital. Storing it took square footage, rather than gigabytes. The music was equally as good, but the cassette format made music that much more valuable.  Even though it is seen as bulky now, at its time it was portable. We bring back the image of storing cassettes in a shoebox. The flipside to storing music on hard drives now.

name: Men's - Heavy Weights (T-Shirt)
description: We sometimes need an extra push to get through hard moments of life. Music has the ability to give this extra push. It sets the tempo to our mood, and helps heighten or change whatever mood we are currently in. Music is inescapable and assists us with everyday battles no matter how big or small. This graphic created is focused around this idea. We compare music to a set of boxing gloves, though both are different, they all assist in the fight. They play similar roles in helping a fighter, and leading the fighter to victory.

name: Men's - Indica (T-Shirt)
description: Many things inspired hip-hop music created during the nineties, but one form of inspiration is obvious. This plant is prominent in content and titles to many great albums, and tracks. We noticed this, and decided to create a shirt paying tribute to this form of inspiration that led to the creation of such great music. The iconic albums of this period would not of came into existence without this plant, and music today would not be the same without these influential albums.

name: Men's - Legends Never Die (T-Shirt)
description: We live our lives not knowing exactly what the meaning is.  Some of us see this aspect of unknowing as a barrier in living a successful and worthwhile life. Some however, choose to live in greatness, innovating and creating, contributing to the world. Rather than living and striving for all things mediocre, they strive for greatness and become legends. The legacy they leave is never forgotten, and their spirit is never dead. We chose The Notorious B.I.G. as inspiration for this design. His persona, and even one of his album titles was built around the idea of ”Life After Death”. He understood that legends never die.

name: Men's - Compton (T-Shirt)
description: The city of Compton has a notorious reputation. Media has showcased the city for all the wrong reasons. We wanted to celebrate the positive aspects of this city. The city is more than what we see; it is the birthplace of great hip-hop. In the nineties, the majority of great hip-hop was being churned out from Compton. One example is the Iconic group NWA, which had members that were legends in their own right. Members like Eazy E, Ice Cube, and Dr. Dre, which created classics with the group as well as on their own. We took inspiration from a familiar video game logo that was creating notable games during that period and meshed it with this inspiring city. Compton creates legends…

name: Men's - Relaxation (T-Shirt)
description: Stress unfortunately is a part of life. Stress hinders creativity, productivity, and makes survival and success in every day life more difficult than it should be. To counter the effects of stress, we must learn how to relax and relieviate stress all together, but that is easier said than done. The secret to relaxation is a controlled state of mind. No element is more effective in controlling the mind in this way than music. Music has the ability to put the mind in ease, bringing up peaceful or happy moments, which in turn put the total mind and body at peace

name: Men's - Self Made (T-Shirt)
description: A person does not come across success just by hoping for it. To achieve true success, an individual needs strength of mind. A person needs to struggle and work hard to reach their fullest potential. The right attitude, self-discipline and the ability to put your goal before your own needs are what are needed. All these factors can only be found in oneself, and nowhere else. There is no substitute for hard work. Luck is not a factor. “The harder you work, the luckier you get.” Many work for a reward or a goal, but sometimes the fact that knowing you accomplished something for yourself is enough. This design is inspired by this concept. The personalized license plate on the front of the design serves as a reminder that the sole fact of making it for oneself is better than any amount of money or fancy vehicle.

name: Men's - Word Is Bond (T-Shirt)
description: Truth is something that will last to eternity without end. This makes a persons word, an important factor during life, and helps in defining what a good person is. A truthful person tends to be a good person, and tends to be someone, which others admire. Deceit and empty promises never bring anything good to the table. Truth however can bring people together, and keep friendships. We took this concept and created this graphic using different opposing teams, putting them together as one. When one’s word is bond, everything is at peace.

name: Men's - Beatz N Hook (T-Shirt)
description: There are many elements that make up a great song. We chose two of these elements as the focus for this design. The two elements chosen are popularly known as the beat and the hook. A good beat sets the tempo for the entire song, and the hook gets the listeners attention announcing the main idea and focus of a song. To showcase the importance of these two elements, we took visual inspiration from our favorite 90’s film Boyz in the Hood. The design was made to fit a similar aesthetic of the film, and we used a typeface known specifically from the hood satire. The final design turned out perfectly, and gave represented both concepts well.

We took inspiration from a familiar video game logo that was creating notable games during that period and meshed it with this inspiring city. Compton creates legends…

name: Mens - Beatz N The Hook (Hooded Pullover)
description: There are many elements that make up a great song. We chose two of these elements as the focus for this design. The two elements chosen are popularly known as the beat and the hook. A good beat sets the tempo for the entire song, and the hook gets the listeners attention announcing the main idea and focus of a song. To showcase the importance of these two elements, we took visual inspiration from our favorite 90’s film Boyz in the Hood. The design was made to fit a similar aesthetic of the film, and we used a typeface known specifically from the hood satire. The final design turned out perfectly, and gave represented both concepts well.

name: Womens - Raised By (S/S Tee)
description: Hip-hop has inspired and changed many lives since it’s creation. It is not only a music genre; it is a culture and lifestyle. We were lucky being able to grow up during an era where hip-hop culture surrounded us.  It was the music we listened to, style of clothing we wore, language we spoke, and way we lived. This positive surrounding and stimulation hip-hop emitted played a part in molding us into who we are today. We pay homage to what hip-hop has given us and created this graphic. We are proud to show that this culture has raised us.

name: Womens - Nostalgia (S/S Tee)
description: Nostalgia is more than just longing for the past; it is factor in our daily lives. Our beliefs in the present are built on the solid foundation of our past. Our surroundings and preferences in the past, helped guide and form who we are now as individuals. We decided to take one memory, which we believe many others can relate to, and created this design. There was a simpler time where music was analog rather than digital. Storing it took square footage, rather than gigabytes. The music was equally as good, but the cassette format made music that much more valuable.  Even though it is seen as bulky now, at its time it was portable. We bring back the image of storing cassettes in a shoebox. The flipside to storing music on hard drives now.

name: Womens - Indica (S/S Tee)
description: Many things inspired hip-hop music created during the nineties, but one form of inspiration is obvious. This plant is prominent in content and titles to many great albums, and tracks. We noticed this, and decided to create a shirt paying tribute to this form of inspiration that led to the creation of such great music. The iconic albums of this period would not of came into existence without this plant, and music today would not be the same without these influential albums.

name: Womens - Legends Never Die (S/S Tee)
description: We live our lives not knowing exactly what the meaning is.  Some of us see this aspect of unknowing as a barrier in living a successful and worthwhile life. Some however, choose to live in greatness, innovating and creating, contributing to the world. Rather than living and striving for all things mediocre, they strive for greatness and become legends. The legacy they leave is never forgotten, and their spirit is never dead. We chose The Notorious B.I.G. as inspiration for this design. His persona, and even one of his album titles was built around the idea of ”Life After Death”. He understood that legends never die.

name: Mens - Crowd Controller (T Shirt)
description: A DJ is much more than people perceive. Those that are not familiar with the art, would think that DJing is just playing music. A DJ is far from that, and is much more complex. A DJ does not just play music, but rather he or she plays off of emotion. This is what separates good DJ’s from Great DJs. A great DJ can read a crowd and select track to play that is guaranteed to change everyone’s vibe or emotions. A DJ is able to control the group they are playing to. The DJ is the crowd controller.

name: Mens - MPC Subway (T-Shirt)
description: The MPC is one of the most coveted pieces of musical equipment in hip-hop history. We place the classic instrument as the focal point of our design. Our interpretation of the MPC includes an aesthetic usually seen on subways. This combination was meant to stress the MPC as a piece of art, not just a machine. The majority of music we love today, would not be the same with out the presence of this piece of art we call the MPC.

name: Mens - Paradise (T-Shirt)
description: Vacation has an important role in everybody’s life. It is something that people need in order to get rid of stress caused by our regular routine. Vacations rejuvenate and revitalize the body, soul and mind and bring us to a deeper state of being human, which is lost from being over worked and stressed. When no pressure is present, we develop personally and creatively. Unfortunately not everyone is able to take a long and extravagant vacation. This is where the power of music comes in. Music has the same ability to rejuvenate and revitalize as taking vacation. Sometimes all we need is to listen to the right track to relax ourselves. Music has the ability to take us to another place with out actually buying a plane ticket. Our design was created to serve as a reminder of this.

name: Mens - LA Strike (T-Shirt)
description: We bring back our popular LA print this season. This is an appropriate piece, being that LA is wonderful during the summer. We figured that our beloved city should be represented all season long since it will be the backdrop of all the great memories we will create this summer. I hope others agree with us as well.

name: Mens - Rhythm Slave (T-Shirt)
description: From the day we are born, we each have rhythm of some sort. As we grow older and progress, we grasp more of the concept of rhythm naturally. Everything in the world is based on some form of rhythm. From the designs of nature, to man made creations such as dancing and music. We are always immersed in rhythm. It makes life that much more beautiful. We understand this and put focus on the beauty that is rhythm in this design. To stress this idea, we placed the beauty of a woman rhythm symbolized by a drum set.

name: Mens - Golden Era (T-Shirt)
description: There was once a period in Hip-Hop that excelled above what we see today as Hip-Hop. This period was a simpler but greater time in hip-hop music based on creativity, pushing the limits, innovation, and the ability to influence. This period created the most influential and greatest hip-hop records in history. We miss this period greatly, but will never forget. This design was meant to serve as a thank you to all the producers, writers, emcees, DJ’s of this great era. We thank you. Your music still lives and will continue to inspire future generations to come.

name: Mens - CA All Day  (T-Shirt)
description: Being that this is our summer collection, we needed to have at least one California inspired design! Notorious for great weather, California is best during the summer. The style of typography and colors chosen were meant to bring across the beauty and peacefulness of this beautiful state during the summer.

name: Mens - Renowned  (T-Shirt)
description: “Luxury” is the focus of this graphic. Luxury is as complicated as it is pricey. What makes something a Luxury item? What adds to the value of the item, compared to others of the same nature? Is the added cost of a luxury item justified? This graphic was created after thinking over some of these questions. We have no exact answer for you, but we can say that value is justified in both the eyes and pocket of the beholder. The concept of luxury has been present in various forms since the beginning of civilization, and relates closely to status and affluence. We just wanted to see how Acrylick would do in this environment and aesthetic. This design is the result. Acrylick doesn’t gravitate or cater towards the elite, and never will. We are for everyone, no matter of status or wealth.

name: Mens - Rise Above (Tank Top)
description:
Rise Above

Nothing can compare to the things that music does to ones soul. It is able to set a mood, as well as change it. If we are feeling down, it has the ability to lift us up.
